# Google Search Console verification
# 1. Go to https://search.google.com/search-console/
# 2. Add property → choose "URL prefix" → enter https://californiaforeverbroker.com
# 3. Select "HTML tag" verification method
# 4. Copy the content value from the <meta> tag shown (e.g. "abc123xyz...")
# 5. Set it here and add .env.local to your deployment environment
GOOGLE_SITE_VERIFICATION=
